Class OutOfReachException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • powerwalk.model.OutOfReachException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class OutOfReachException
extends java.lang.Exception
    An exception that is thrown when an action involves moving towards an unreachable destination.
